examples.en: He was the commander of the Pacific fleet.

examples.en: A commander in each county was to have charge of the local militia.

examples.en: The government has accepted the resignation of a senior army commander.

examples.en: The commander rallied his troops for a counterattack.
examples.ru: Командующий собрал свои войска для контратаки.

examples.en: The military commander was exfiltrated on a French plane.

examples.en: The naval commander disengaged the two largest ships from the sea battle.
examples.ru: Адмирал вывел из боя два самых больших корабля.

examples.en: The army post's stern commander always had the utmost respect of those who served under him.
examples.ru: Этот строгий командир воинской части всегда питал величайшее уважение к тем, кто служил под его началом.
